<p>Camelia is the spokesbug for Perl 6, the spunky fast-growing sister of Perl 5.
Like her world-famous big sister, Perl 6 intends to carry forward the high
ideals of the Perl community.</p>

<p>Perl 6 is currently being developed further by a team of dedicated and
enthusiastic volunteers. You can help too. The only requirement is that you
know how to be nice to all kinds of people (and butterflies). Go to #perl6
(irc.freenode.net) and someone will be glad to help you get started.</p>
</div>


